# Online_quiz_game

Description:
An interactive and responsive online quiz application designed to provide users with a seamless and engaging experience while taking quizzes. This project was developed during my internship to enhance my skills in front-end development, user interface design, and JavaScript programming.

Features
Responsive Design:

The application is fully responsive, ensuring a smooth user experience across various devices, including desktops, tablets, and mobile phones.
Utilized CSS media queries to adjust the layout and elements dynamically based on screen size.
Dynamic Content Loading:

Questions and answer choices are dynamically loaded from a JavaScript object, allowing for easy updates and maintenance.
Implemented a function to shuffle questions and choices to provide a unique experience for each quiz attempt.
User Interaction:

Added functionality for users to select and highlight their answers, providing immediate visual feedback.
A "Submit" button to finalize the answer, with validation to ensure an answer is selected before submission.
Score Calculation and Display:

The application calculates the user's score based on the correct answers and displays the result at the end of the quiz.
Implemented a dedicated score display section that appears after the quiz is completed, showing the total score and correct answers.
Feedback on Selection:

Immediate feedback is provided by showing the selected answer on the screen, enhancing user engagement and interactivity.
This feature helps users keep track of their choices before submitting their final answer.
User-Friendly Interface:

Designed a clean and intuitive interface with easy navigation to ensure users can focus on the quiz without distractions.
Utilized CSS for styling and animations to enhance the visual appeal of the application.

Technologies Used
HTML, CSS, JS with the help of VS Code
